This page lists my projects:

* [BlenSor](http://www.blensor.org): Blender sensor simulation ([github](https://github.com/mgschwan/blensor))
* [pyWiggle](http://mgschwan.github.com/pyWiggle): Stereoview interpolation
* [ThereTV](http://theretv.zero997.com): Android client for the Sony Location Free protocol ([Android market](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mgschwan.fxreg&feature=more_from_developer#?t=W251bGwsMSwyLDEwMiwiY29tLm1nc2Nod2FuLmZ4cmVnIl0.)
* [polyran](https://code.google.com/p/polyran/): C++ library for robust fitting of N-th order polynomials
using RANSAC
